title: Match of the Day 2014-02-08 720p 50fps HDTV x264-wAm.mkv
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD  
Date: Saturday 8th February 2014

Gary Lineker presents highlights of the day's eight Premier League matches. Title hopefuls Liverpool and Arsenal meet at Anfield, where the Gunners have been unbeaten in their last six visits. Chelsea vie to maintain their title push at the expense of a Newcastle side, who deservedly won the reverse fixture in November, while Manchester City travel to Norwich, who suffered a club record-equalling 7-0 defeat when the sides last met. In the late kick-off, new Cardiff City manager Ole Gunnar Solskjaer takes his side to Swansea for the south Wales derby.

Captured and encoded at 50fps to give much smoother movement.
